{
  "id": "adv_event_2111_01_01",
  "title": "夢踊るステージに架け橋を 1話 家族の存在",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ふぅっ、今日のレッスンはここまでにしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ let’s end today’s lesson there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、だいぶ息が上がってきてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re both out of breath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ～っ、助かった～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* That’s a relief!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんとのレッスンはいつもハードだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lessons with you are always tough‚ Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぜえぜえ、め、芽衣は、練習不足ですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*wheeze* Y-you’re out of practice‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "この程度のれ、れ、レッスンで音を上げるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Complaining already in s-such an easy lesson…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう？　すずはまだまだ元気なのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? So you still have plenty of energy‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ練習メニューを見直さないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ looks like I’ll have to review the lesson menu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひぃー！　ごめんなさい、私、見栄を張りました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek! Sorry‚ I was just trying to show off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "怜のダンスレッスンは、スパルタ過ぎますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your dance lessons are too extreme for me‚ Rei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あはは、怜ちゃんは凄いよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Rei-chan‚ you’re awesome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も足がくがくだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My legs are all wobbly too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう言いつつ、芽衣はまだ余裕がありそうですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ Mei‚ but it looks like you still have some in the tank…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私から見たら、二人とも体力おばけですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From where I’m standing‚ you both look like muscle monsters…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "やっぱり怜ちゃんは、基礎体力が芽衣達とは違うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I figure that your physical fitness is on a totally different level from ours‚ Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ダンス大会で優勝したことあるんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve won at dance tournaments‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……あんなの大したことないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That kind of thing is no big deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その謙遜した態度がかえって怜を凄く見せますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That humble attitude just makes you look more awesome‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私もそんな風に言ってみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like to try talking like that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "謙遜じゃないわ。本当に、あんなの意味がなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not being humble. Really‚ it didn’t mean anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why ever not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんとかお母さん、喜んでくれなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Weren’t your parents happy about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.83333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人には話してなかったっけ……全然よ。だから私は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have I never told you two about it? They showed no reaction.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと大きな舞台を求めて、アイドルになったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I went looking for a much bigger stage‚ and became an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でもいまだに認めてもらえてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they still don’t acknowledge me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "特に父とは冷戦状態よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In particular‚ it’s like a cold war with my father.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え！　NEXT VENUSグランプリで優勝したのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "認めてもらえないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and they still won’t acknowledge you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええ。そもそも芸能活動自体、よく思ってないみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It looks like they just don’t like the idea of how show business works.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと軽薄な仕事だと思ってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure they think it’s just a frivolous job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "芽衣の家族は応援してくれてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei's family supports Mei‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも同じだと思ってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I thought everybody was the same…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は縁を切られているようなものよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like they’ve disowned me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "たまに母から連絡が来るくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My mother gets in touch sometimes‚ but that’s all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルはみんなを元気にする素敵なお仕事ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being an idol is a wonderful job that cheers everyone up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "決して軽薄なんかじゃありませんのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s certainly not “frivolous”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "仕方ないわ、頭が固い人だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can’t be helped‚ they’re stubborn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
